Then {CoG:get destroyed}<br>
<br>
My point being this - you can not &quot;zerg&quot; this dragon whatsoever.. anyone under level 55 will basically be res fodder, simply because of his spells/effects/whatever. Main stats to buff/build/work on for this type of a raid: MR/PR/DR. They are critical, as he is a shaman-based dragon, and if any of you have ever battled a shaman in the arena (or wherever) that was buffed, had a pet, and was FM, you *know* what they can do if you do not resist his/her spells. At lvl 55, I was flat out waisted by a 51 shaman because he was able to land a couple dot's. <br>
<br>
***Do not skimp on the resists.*** <br>
